titles.title: Dredge Records for Knorr Cruise 210, Leg 5 to the Mid-Atlantic Ridge between 16° and 17°N

resource.publisher: EarthChem Library(ECL) | Interdisciplinary Earth Data Alliance (IEDA) | Columbia University; doi:10.17616/R3V644

rightsList.rights: Creative Commons Attribution-NonCommercial-Share Alike 3.0 United States [CC BY-NC-SA 3.0]

descriptions.description: This dataset describes the dredge records for Knorr Cruise 210 Leg 5 to the Mid-Atlantic Ridge between 16° and 17°N. There are three files: (1) Dredge Locations: the navigation records for the dredge, a brief location description, and a summary of what was dredge and how much of each. (2) Dredge Summary: a detailed summation by specific rock type for each dredge of what was collected. (3) Dredge Rock Descriptions: the detailed information on each rock sample described on the cruise, and how much undescribed material there is.
